Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.66,0:00:20.19,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Louise...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.96,0:00:25.61,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Louise, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.61,0:00:28.63,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Even in your dreams, \Nyou want to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.63,0:00:32.76,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you love me so much, \Nyou just can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.80,0:00:35.65,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Now beg.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.65,0:00:39.00,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Say, "I am my owner's puppy."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.25,0:00:41.03,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.03,0:00:43.41,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what he wants me to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.13,0:00:46.36,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,What a naughty dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.16,0:00:50.39,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm a kind master, and \Nsince it's just a dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.39,0:00:51.99,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let that one slip.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.27,0:00:56.81,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,An unobstructed, flat plain...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.21,0:01:03.78,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,And now the mountain range...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.26,0:01:10.09,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Louise, what was that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.11,0:01:12.28,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,T-Tabitha?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.76,0:01:14.92,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.92,0:01:15.65,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,Guarding him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.65,0:01:17.56,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Saito's knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.56,0:01:18.70,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Stay out of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.70,0:01:20.02,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,This dog here,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.02,0:01:23.32,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,dared to touch my breasts and \Ncompare them to a flat plain!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.82,0:01:25.96,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,I would be happy about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.12,0:01:29.88,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, it's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.88,0:01:31.40,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Though mine are indeed a mountain range.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.69,0:01:35.08,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,You were awake, weren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.58,0:01:38.71,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,What's important to \Nremember here is that both
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.71,0:01:40.85,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,the plains and the mountains \Nare equally wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.85,0:01:43.63,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Saito, are you really sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.73,0:01:47.85,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Well, maybe the mountains are \Njust a tiny bit more wonderful...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.06,0:01:55.29,CRZero,Colbert,0000,0000,0000,,Saito, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.91,0:01:57.63,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Professor Colbert!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.40,0:02:00.15,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing up so early?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.06,0:02:03.78,CRZero,Colbert,0000,0000,0000,,I actually came to tell \Nyou something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.78,0:02:04.80,CRZero,Colbert,0000,0000,0000,,All of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.67,0:02:08.00,CRZero,Colbert,0000,0000,0000,,It appears that
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.00,0:02:10.31,CRZero,Colbert,0000,0000,0000,,we're all off again on another \Ntrip aboard the Ostland.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.80,0:02:13.98,CRZero,Colbert,0000,0000,0000,,Queen Henrietta has ordered \Nus all to Romalia.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.79,0:02:15.92,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Romalia?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.11,0:03:52.03,Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)}Louise of the Holy Land
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.38,0:04:13.67,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Vallière, you must be so \Nhappy that we're going to Romalia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.67,0:04:16.83,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! Romalia is the \Ncenter of the Brimir faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.47,0:04:21.64,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,A pious follower of Brimir like \Nmyself is happy just to go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.14,0:04:24.33,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Then if you're happy enough as it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.33,0:04:26.79,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,may Saito and I go on a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.79,0:04:27.79,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,That's a no.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.20,0:04:29.11,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,You scrooge.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.11,0:04:31.90,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,The Fire Dragon Mountains \Nare so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.90,0:04:34.91,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,Strong and indomitable, just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.91,0:04:37.92,CRZero,Colbert,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is that so, Miss Zerbst?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.92,0:04:41.76,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,This truly is Halkeginia's \Nmost renowned mountain range.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.76,0:04:43.32,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.49,0:04:46.40,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Tiffa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.48,0:04:48.70,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,You're sighing a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.70,0:04:49.88,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.88,0:04:52.41,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,No. I was just wondering \Nwhy the princess
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.41,0:04:54.34,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,would possibly summon me to Romalia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.34,0:04:55.12,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.12,0:04:57.31,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,She's called for Louise, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.31,0:04:59.39,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,They're letting us use this ship
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.39,0:05:01.03,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,and calling it an educational school trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.03,0:05:02.68,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,We're all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.68,0:05:06.45,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,The Brimir worshipers never \Nthought highly of the elves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.08,0:05:09.95,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,It's natural for a half-elf like \Nyou to be a little nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.95,0:05:12.06,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.52,0:05:14.14,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.42,0:05:17.07,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.07,0:05:19.90,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,If push comes to shove, I'll protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.34,0:05:22.75,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.87,0:05:30.94,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies and gentlemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.66,0:05:33.08,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.58,0:05:37.09,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,It's Romalia!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.67,0:05:40.71,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies and gentlemen of the \NOrder of the Undine Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:44.49,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,This journey is a secret mission \Nfor Her Highness the Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.71,0:05:47.93,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what dangers we may face,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.93,0:05:51.63,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,so long as I remain your captain, \Nyou have nothing to fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.83,0:05:54.16,CRZero,Malicorne,0000,0000,0000,,Was this really something that big?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:55.44,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.44,0:05:57.07,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,Dear students of magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.95,0:05:59.37,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to greet you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.37,0:06:01.58,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,at the end of your journey and wish \Nyou a warm welcome to Romalia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.14,0:06:04.20,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while, Saito.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.20,0:06:05.28,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Julio!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.69,0:06:08.44,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot you're a Romalian priest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.44,0:06:09.95,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.95,0:06:12.82,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,I was asked to properly welcome you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.30,0:06:14.83,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'll leave them with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.69,0:06:19.27,CRZero,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you to the guest house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:20.49,CRZero,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,Please follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.47,0:06:24.93,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,Saito, I'd like you to come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.08,0:06:29.30,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,Along with Miss Vallière and Miss Westwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.31,0:06:47.86,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Look, it's Romalia's biggest cathedral.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.67,0:06:52.33,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,May I ask why only us three have been called?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.33,0:06:55.91,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,It is the express wish of our queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.91,0:06:58.51,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,Hers, and another's.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.80,0:06:59.66,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Another?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.33,0:07:27.51,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,Louise, Saito,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.06,0:07:28.90,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,Tiffania,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.90,0:07:30.41,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.20,0:07:34.70,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.33,0:07:37.33,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Was it really okay for us to come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.77,0:07:40.22,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't the Tristain coffers pretty empty?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.77,0:07:42.24,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.88,0:07:45.30,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about money. \NRomalia's covering the expenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.30,0:07:47.51,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could be so naïve!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.18,0:07:49.49,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.49,0:07:50.50,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,Julio.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.50,0:07:52.35,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,You're being very rude to our guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.72,0:08:05.33,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,My apologies, Your Eminence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.33,0:08:08.04,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing them made me feel like I \Nwas back at the academy again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.04,0:08:09.03,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Your Eminence?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.03,0:08:11.27,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito! Put your head down, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.69,0:08:14.24,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,You are in the presence \Nof His Holy Eminence!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.02,0:08:17.31,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,And who is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.57,0:08:20.89,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,So you're Saito Chevalier de Hiraga.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.32,0:08:23.54,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,Every bit as unconventional \Nas the rumors say you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.09,0:08:26.28,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,It certainly is true that you've \Ncome from another world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.95,0:08:29.77,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,Please, raise your heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.16,0:08:33.36,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to see your faces better.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.61,0:08:41.87,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,I am Vittorio Serevare, also known as
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.87,0:08:46.36,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,Pope of Romalia, Saint Aegis the 32nd.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.36,0:08:48.34,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.82,0:08:51.58,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,Both the Void Mage and her familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.48,0:08:53.35,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Your Eminence!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.69,0:08:54.68,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,How did you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.17,0:09:00.12,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,The tales of your bravery have \Nreached even Romalia, Miss Vallière.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.58,0:09:05.62,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,I've always known that you are the \Nbearer of the legendary power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.48,0:09:09.36,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,This is such an honor, Your Eminence.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:12.50,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,And then you, Miss Westwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.17,0:09:16.53,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,You're probably not aware of this yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.53,0:09:19.26,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,but you are also a Void Mage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.31,0:09:22.81,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that you have \Nnot found a familiar yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.60,0:09:26.93,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,but your Mind Wipe magic \Nis more than enough proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.27,0:09:30.49,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,So that means I'm like Louise?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.97,0:09:32.78,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,And there's another one of you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.22,0:09:37.10,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,I am also a Void Mage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.11,0:09:42.27,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, all three of \Nus possess the legendary magic
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.27,0:09:45.30,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,given to us so that we may lead others.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.30,0:09:46.30,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,We are kindred spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.62,0:09:51.27,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,We are kindred spirits with Your Eminence?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.08,0:09:55.12,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,And he is my familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.78,0:09:59.50,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,I am God's right hand, Windalfr.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.96,0:10:02.18,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,I can freely control the beasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.80,0:10:04.68,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,That puts you and me together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:06.79,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,You and me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.06,0:10:10.43,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,The three Void magicians
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.43,0:10:14.01,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,and their two familiars \Nare in one place at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.27,0:10:18.36,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,Now I will ask Her Royal \NHighness to take over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.22,0:10:20.97,CRZero,Hen,0000,0000,0000,,Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.97,0:10:21.83,CRZero,Hen,0000,0000,0000,,Tiffania.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.34,0:10:24.13,CRZero,Hen,0000,0000,0000,,We will soon be celebrating
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.13,0:10:26.67,CRZero,Hen,0000,0000,0000,,the third anniversary of \NHis Holiness's ascent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.11,0:10:29.66,CRZero,Hen,0000,0000,0000,,His Holiness requests your \Npresence as his shrine maidens
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.66,0:10:32.58,CRZero,Hen,0000,0000,0000,,and he will also ask \Nyou to pray with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.54,0:10:34.99,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,He's asking us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.57,0:10:37.88,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,But what does that have to do with the Void?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.44,0:10:42.73,CRZero,Hen,0000,0000,0000,,We hope to garner the attention \Nof the fourth user this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.04,0:10:44.94,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,The fourth?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.94,0:10:47.53,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,You know him, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.84,0:10:49.53,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,Joseph, the king of Gallia.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.48,0:10:51.70,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,The Joseph who...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.96,0:10:52.83,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.83,0:10:54.90,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,He is an inhumane man who killed
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:57.54,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,Tabitha's father and destroyed \Nher mother's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.99,0:11:00.30,CRZero,Illococoo,0000,0000,0000,,It's still not dinner time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.53,0:11:02.56,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.56,0:11:06.28,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to show that same \NKing Joseph something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.85,0:11:10.32,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps he will change his \Nways if he sees that the other
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.80,0:11:13.92,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,three Void Mages have joined forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.44,0:11:17.21,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one who did something \Nthat horrible to Tabitha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.21,0:11:19.01,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,How could we ever hope to—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.50,0:11:21.35,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,If it does not happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.35,0:11:25.36,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,Halkeginia will face a crisis \Nas it has never before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.36,0:11:26.31,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Crisis?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.31,0:11:28.03,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,It is the duty of Void Mages
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.03,0:11:30.34,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,to join forces in order to save Halkeginia.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.39,0:11:35.51,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,The reason that the Void Mages \Nare here points to the fact
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.51,0:11:37.91,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,that an event is approaching that needs them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.35,0:11:44.32,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,The fate of the world is, \Nquite literally, in our hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.04,0:11:47.42,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,The fate of the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.81,0:11:53.49,CRZero,Hen,0000,0000,0000,,Please consider whether or not \Nyou will be shrine maidens.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.49,0:11:55.29,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,No, Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.85,0:11:58.10,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,There is no reason to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.79,0:11:59.76,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I will do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.34,0:12:01.70,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I will become His Eminence's shrine maiden!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.09,0:12:03.10,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Louise...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.98,0:12:11.76,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies and gentlemen of the \NOrder of the Undine Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.76,0:12:13.98,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,Let us restore our energy for tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.33,0:12:16.02,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,To Her Majesty, Queen Henrietta!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.69,0:12:18.28,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,To His Holy Eminence!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.28,0:12:21.52,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,And to us, Undines!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.22,0:12:28.04,CRZero,Jacques,0000,0000,0000,,Quite the noisy crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.04,0:12:30.52,CRZero,Jeanette,0000,0000,0000,,They're just lively, Jacques.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.87,0:12:33.03,CRZero,Jeanette,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we make a toast, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.35,0:12:34.41,CRZero,Doudou,0000,0000,0000,,An excellent idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.41,0:12:36.57,CRZero,Doudou,0000,0000,0000,,Let's drink to future riches!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.57,0:12:38.14,CRZero,Doudou,0000,0000,0000,,Jeanette, order something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.54,0:12:41.19,CRZero,Jaqcues,0000,0000,0000,,First we've got work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.70,0:12:42.74,CRZero,Jaqcues,0000,0000,0000,,Get everything ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.27,0:12:44.48,CRZero,Doudou,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.48,0:12:46.51,CRZero,Doudou,0000,0000,0000,,You're no fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.83,0:12:49.73,CRZero,Jacques,0000,0000,0000,,I'm off, Big Brother Damian.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.68,0:12:53.12,CRZero,Dam,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.75,0:13:04.62,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Louise, are you really going to do
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.62,0:13:06.05,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,what the Pope's asking?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.05,0:13:07.33,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.74,0:13:09.30,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,A noblewoman never goes back on her word.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.95,0:13:12.68,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,But you know what that guy did to Tabitha.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.99,0:13:14.74,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,We have no idea what he's going to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.05,0:13:16.33,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.33,0:13:17.91,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,You may be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.91,0:13:20.26,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,But listen, Saito.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.26,0:13:21.58,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I really want to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.58,0:13:22.08,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.49,0:13:25.53,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,You mean you're totally gaga over him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.33,0:13:28.25,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.48,0:13:30.01,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.01,0:13:32.42,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,"Oh, Your Holiness!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:36.76,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Any follower of Brimir would \Nbe starstruck to meet him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.76,0:13:38.19,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.41,0:13:40.39,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,All I'm saying is that you may have answered
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.39,0:13:41.53,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,before properly thinking it through.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.82,0:13:44.61,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true! I did—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.61,0:13:46.72,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Well, maybe it's fine for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.49,0:13:49.94,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,but you might have put Tiffa on the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.94,0:13:51.88,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,She's not a follower of Brimir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.16,0:13:56.18,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,She was probably all confused, \Nhaving just been told
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.18,0:13:57.62,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,that she's a Void Mage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.04,0:13:59.92,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't have a familiar yet, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.92,0:14:01.79,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what this is about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.18,0:14:04.96,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,You don't care at all about how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.96,0:14:07.08,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,All you care about are Tiffa's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.08,0:14:08.36,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but Tiffa...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:09.85,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,It's just Tiffa, Tiffa, Tiffa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.85,0:14:14.62,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,If you like Tiffa so much, why \Ndon't you just become her familiar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.80,0:14:17.87,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,You know, if I could, I would!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.14,0:14:21.08,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Fine! Then there's no \Nreason for you to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.08,0:14:23.27,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Get out, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.27,0:14:24.54,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to tell me twice!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.35,0:14:36.50,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,It must have been quite a shock to suddenly
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.50,0:14:37.99,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,find out you're a Void Mage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.38,0:14:40.93,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,I still can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.44,0:14:43.61,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I want to give you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.97,0:14:45.00,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.92,0:14:52.77,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.31,0:14:54.82,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.82,0:14:58.11,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,This ring was originally passed \Ndown in the House of Albion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.83,0:15:02.25,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,You're the last one of that \Nblood, and you possess the magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.02,0:15:06.10,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,This belongs with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.63,0:15:10.99,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Why is Saito such an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.26,0:15:18.61,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.52,0:15:26.30,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,I do want to be of help to everybody...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.84,0:15:28.27,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,But what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.54,0:15:30.44,CRZero,Colbert,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Westwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.44,0:15:32.13,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,Professor Colbert!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.59,0:15:34.88,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,You're staying here, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.21,0:15:38.09,CRZero,Colbert,0000,0000,0000,,No, I actually came here on an errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.09,0:15:39.39,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.88,0:15:41.59,CRZero,Colbert,0000,0000,0000,,Goodnight, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.59,0:15:42.85,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,Goodnight, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.84,0:15:47.89,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,Professor Colbert!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.41,0:15:50.77,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,May I ask you a favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.28,0:15:55.50,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,Please show me the ritual \Nof summoning a familiar!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.86,0:15:59.51,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't get what her problem is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.58,0:16:03.91,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,All I was asking her to do was \Nto think about Tiffa a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.55,0:16:06.85,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Then she says "Well then, why \Ndon't you be {\i1}her{\i0} familiar?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.37,0:16:10.58,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,After she was all swooning over the Pope!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.99,0:16:14.17,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Saito,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.17,0:16:17.78,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,in all honesty, it makes me happy to hear
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.78,0:16:21.09,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,that you're fighting with Miss Vallière.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.09,0:16:21.69,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.07,0:16:22.92,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.92,0:16:25.99,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Since I do acknowledge Miss \NVallière as a rival for your love,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.99,0:16:28.44,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,I can say that I don't believe she would
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.44,0:16:30.34,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,ever be swooning for anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.89,0:16:33.71,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,It's not even possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.71,0:16:36.26,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you might be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.26,0:16:37.15,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I'm right!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.69,0:16:40.21,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,That means you've got to think this over!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.80,0:16:43.47,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,You have to think about why \Nit's so important for her
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.47,0:16:45.48,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,to honor the Pope's request so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.48,0:16:48.75,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, but I've got no clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.75,0:16:50.62,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,You really don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.27,0:16:53.49,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,She's the one who was called Louise the Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.82,0:16:55.10,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,After she was told that she
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.10,0:16:57.30,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,could save the world if \Nshe tried hard enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.30,0:16:59.16,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,do you think she could not try?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.13,0:17:03.41,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.93,0:17:05.62,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Siesta!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.23,0:17:12.68,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,This is the only time I'm \Nhelping you, Miss Vallière.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.84,0:17:27.36,CRZero,Jacques,0000,0000,0000,,The Mirror of our Founders, you're certain?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.65,0:17:30.30,CRZero,Doudou,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we take some other goodies, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.78,0:17:32.28,CRZero,Doudou,0000,0000,0000,,We could get some good money for these.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.62,0:17:34.57,CRZero,Jacques,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch anything but \Nwhat we were ordered to get.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.43,0:17:37.77,CRZero,Doudou,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you would say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.59,0:17:42.19,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm glad I followed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.19,0:17:44.57,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Too bad Saito's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.02,0:17:49.39,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But against these two, \NI'll be fine, even by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.75,0:17:51.55,CRZero,Jacques,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.11,0:18:04.19,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Help! Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.53,0:18:07.27,CRZero,Jacques,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do anything stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.00,0:18:12.25,CRZero,Doudou,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, she's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.30,0:18:18.24,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Someone, help!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.17,0:18:21.32,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Did I just hear something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.64,0:18:23.12,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.12,0:18:23.78,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Louise?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.94,0:18:26.68,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Please, come here, Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.16,0:18:31.15,CRZero,Jacques,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.83,0:18:32.42,CRZero,Doudou,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.78,0:18:34.63,CRZero,Jacques,0000,0000,0000,,The mirror is enough for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.45,0:18:45.47,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.47,0:18:47.65,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito, they're thieves!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.05,0:18:52.77,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do to her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.65,0:18:55.78,CRZero,Doudou,0000,0000,0000,,Relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.78,0:18:58.35,CRZero,Doudou,0000,0000,0000,,It's not what you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.19,0:19:05.52,CRZero,Jacques,0000,0000,0000,,I'll deal with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.52,0:19:06.91,CRZero,Jacques,0000,0000,0000,,You take that and run.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.91,0:19:07.93,CRZero,Doudou,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.93,0:19:09.59,CRZero,Doudou,0000,0000,0000,,You're always treating me like a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.96,0:19:15.77,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.77,0:19:17.00,CRZero,Derflinger,0000,0000,0000,,One's coming from above, partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.19,0:19:41.45,CRZero,Derflinger,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.45,0:19:43.56,CRZero,Derflinger,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like this guy's quite skilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.56,0:19:46.00,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,So what?! I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.51,0:19:52.28,CRZero,Colbert,0000,0000,0000,,The Summon Servant is not \Nsuch a difficult spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.28,0:19:54.07,CRZero,Colbert,0000,0000,0000,,Focus your spirit and then call
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.07,0:19:56.34,CRZero,Colbert,0000,0000,0000,,on your yet unseen familiar in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.90,0:19:57.73,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.52,0:20:02.94,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Tiffania Westwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.45,0:20:06.27,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,Pentagon of the five powers,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.27,0:20:09.82,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,obey my fate and summon my familiar!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.23,0:20:21.58,CRZero,Jacques,0000,0000,0000,,You're not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.58,0:20:22.33,CRZero,Jacques,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.11,0:20:36.43,CRZero,Jacques,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take this personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.14,0:20:40.49,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Louise, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.49,0:20:41.16,CRZero,Jacques,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.87,0:20:43.28,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Explosion!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.39,0:21:06.41,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,The gate is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.90,0:21:10.92,CRZero,Colbert,0000,0000,0000,,Levitation!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.30,0:21:13.89,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.33,0:21:15.03,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.03,0:21:16.40,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.92,0:21:17.72,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.73,0:21:26.15,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Professor, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.15,0:21:29.08,CRZero,Colbert,0000,0000,0000,,It was no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.90,0:21:38.18,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Louise,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.93,0:21:43.16,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,were you really planning to fight \Nthose guys all by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.96,0:21:47.15,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault for leaving \Nme alone like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.44,0:21:49.25,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who told me to get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.25,0:21:52.24,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I was so scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.62,0:21:56.46,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess as a Void Mage, \NI am responsible for this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.45,0:21:59.87,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,So I figured I'd have to try, even by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.49,0:22:01.97,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, you're so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.97,0:22:04.21,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.21,0:22:05.70,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, maybe not stupid, just reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.01,0:22:08.84,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you talk to your master like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.28,0:22:10.15,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.15,0:22:11.88,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,You're my master,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.88,0:22:14.81,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,so you need to take advantage \Nof your familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.84,0:22:19.35,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,It's your duty to depend on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.55,0:22:22.68,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,The weight of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.68,0:22:25.35,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,might be a little lighter if \Nit's shared between two people.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.35,0:22:26.36,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.42,0:22:47.89,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,It's not what it looks like, Tiffa!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.69,0:22:52.18,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,This dog doesn't care who he \Ngets it from when he's in heat!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.46,0:22:54.98,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're the one who started it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.98,0:22:57.64,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Are you going to say I asked for it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.64,0:22:58.93,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,You did!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.93,0:23:01.53,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who closed your eyes \Nand made the kissy lips!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.53,0:23:04.12,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I most certainly did not!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.12,0:23:05.16,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you did!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.16,0:23:06.00,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Did not!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.00,0:23:06.87,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Did too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.00,0:23:08.00,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yesterday, I could've sworn
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.00,0:23:10.54,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I saw Saito disappear into that portal,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.90,0:23:12.56,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but I must have imagined it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.56,0:23:13.27,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Did too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.27,0:23:14.41,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Did not!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.50,0:23:17.71,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whenever I see him, though, \Nmy heart starts beating so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.03,0:23:18.96,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.96,0:23:22.44,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, I was not\Nasking you to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.29,0:23:30.45,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to work hard as \Nthe Pope's shrine maiden!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.45,0:23:35.30,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess I could grant Saito a little \Ntime alone with me before then.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.30,0:23:37.10,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Aquileia's Shrine Maiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.86,0:23:41.00,Next-Ep-Title,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(955,0)}Aquileia's Shrine Maiden
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.10,0:23:39.90,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, who or what is Lemon?
